review_text: This is a nice park with splashpad and play areas for different ages and a basketball court. There's also many trees so it's well shaded.
It is a wonderful park fir kids
Good water playground , only problem Kids riding bike run over smaller kids even when is forbidden riding bikes inside water playground and parents doesn't care
The playground equipment maybe is a bit older, five or so years maybe, but the splash pad was AWESOME!!!
Great little park to play with the kids, awesome water fountain
Fun place on the right day ,,, lot of activities  ,,  for everyone
Nice, clean and good views of the canal.
Nice for kids of all ages

(Translated by Google) Large park with fun children's modules. In addition to a moving bus and a hickey that allows a child and an adult to have fun together!

(Original)
Grand parc avec des modules pour enfants amusants. En plus d'un autobus qui bouge et un suçon qui permet à un enfant et un adulte de s'amuser ensemble!

(Translated by Google) Super park with different levels of games for children. The water games could be a bit more modern than a fountain but at least it does the trick!

Super parc avec différents niveaux de jeux pour les enfants.  Les jeux d'eau pourraient être un peu plus moderne qu'une fontaine mais au moins, ça fait l'affaire!
